Name: django-form-tags
Version: 2.1
Summary: Django templatetags to easily render fieldholders, fieldwrappers and fields.
Home-page: https://gitlab.com/mediamoose/django-form-tags/tree/v2.1
Author: Sven Groot (Mediamoose)
Author-email: sven@mediamoose.nl
